<plot>This documentary tells the story of the staging of Franco Zeffirelli's 'Tosca' with Maria Callas at Covent Garden - a story that encapsulates the highs and lows of her career, the public triumph and personal tragedy that was the life of the most loved and admired opera star of them all; a life ending in lost nerve, lost voice and lost love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?357835</url></doc>
